This is a Weather app created with JavaScript. It fetchs live weather data from Open Weather Map API.

Author: Wairimu Kuria Contact: mimokuria@gmail.com or wairimukuria@eliveltd.com

DESCRIPTION:This project is built using HTML in design and CSS and Javascript to make the website presentable and colorful.

INSTALLATION Just follow the following steps to have it in your computer. Google https://wairimu2018.github.io/Phase-1-Project/ git clone on your directory(local computer) -Open command line and then type the following line. $ git clone https://wairimu2018.github.io/Phase-1-Project/.

